        {
            "+content": "Narukami Ryusei is your typical NEET. He spends his days shut in his room playing video games without a care in the world, living a lazy life. But the truth is, Ryusei used to be a powerful demon king in another world. He wants to spend this new life doing whatever he wants, except that he wasn't the only one reincarnated into this world. The hero who struck him down is here too—and she's a really cute high school girl.",
